The paper focuses on the integration of vision and language tasks, which involves deep learning, computer vision, and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing. The paper also discusses methods and datasets related to computer vision, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning, which is a popular technique in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
